群体不下数百人；在全国，这个数字要翻上几番。他们损害了城市营商环境，搅乱了招聘市场秩序，也挑战着法律的尊严。3 年在沪买别墅，同时供职 16 家公司却从不上班，落网时她还在面试"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-bc076c9bba4cb7d1525f8071541b8e7c_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "371 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619972219"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8I3ggubTvflqEAMaCTEwMDA1MTQxOCDVisCnBjAAOIECQARyCTYxOTk3MjIxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1693630946.239730", "card_id": "Q_619675304", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在观看诺兰新片《奥本海默》前，了解哪些信息可以更好地理解这部真实事件改编的电影？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-30dd8bfdbadaeda4a3f042a6fb1b283f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "242 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619675304"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "诺兰回答", "font_color": "GYL02A", "background": "GYL02A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8I3ggubTvflqEAMaCDk5OTg1NjEwIP2qtqcGMAA4sQFABXIJNjE5Njc1MzA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1693630946.240141", "card_id": "Q_620151847", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中超武汉三镇投资人停止注资，俱乐部发布 41 页招商 PPT 进行自救，如何看待这样的举动，能有效吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "根据此前的消息，9 月 1 日，武汉三镇的投资人就不再为俱乐部注资。在今天，武汉三镇在各大平台发布了一份「招商 PPT」，积极展开自救。招商 PPT？武汉三镇发布长篇「自我介绍」吸引投资"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4f64200e90a0885b6f9eaa1df1c9c8b8_b.jpg"}, "metr